casebody.data:
James Packard v. Department of Motor Vehicles (10681)

Landau, Heiman and Schaller, Js.

Argued December 4 decision released December 29, 1992 Raymond T. Trebisacci, for the appellant (plaintiff). Priscilla J. Green, assistant attorney general, with whom, on the brief, was Richard Blumenthal, attorney general, for the appellee (defendant). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
